node.text: I HATE when they say that! But all makes us stronger 💕

𝐇𝐞𝐫𝐞’𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐧𝐠,𝐰𝐞 𝐠𝐨 𝐚𝐛𝐨𝐯𝐞 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐛𝐞𝐲𝐨𝐧𝐝 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐩𝐞𝐨𝐩𝐥𝐞 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐰𝐞 𝐚𝐫𝐞 𝐨𝐟𝐭𝐞𝐧 𝐛𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐢𝐫 𝐛𝐨𝐮𝐧𝐝𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐞𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐨𝐰𝐧.We over give while continuing to settle for someone else not showing up.⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
While going above and beyond can be loving ,it is often at the cost of ourselves .Don’t get me wrong there are times when someone is in real need of support .But when we are continuously going to the moon and back,we are actually robbing them of the chance to do their own work.We are left empty and resentful that we have nothing for ourselves.Always protect your energy !⁣⁣
𝘊𝘰𝘮𝘮𝘦𝘯𝘵 𝘥𝘰𝘸𝘯 𝘣𝘦𝘭𝘰𝘸 𝘪𝘧 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘢𝘨𝘳𝘦𝘦
